
Event loop: 

	[x] Use pyserial to wait for button press

	[] Do nothing (some vis/screensaver??) until button press

	[] On button press:
		[] Start 3 second countdown onscreen (as fast as we can render!!)
		[] after 3 seconds, launch gphoto2 to take picture (may need lead time)
		[] Show spinner to user, wait for gphoto2 to take

		[] create thumbnail, display onscreen for at least 30 seconds, 
